    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics and
      pharmacodynamics of a single dose of ALN-TTR01 in patients with transthyretin (TTR) mediated
      amyloidosis (ATTR).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
